alfredsnippet.name: Get size of arrays, objects or strings.
alfredsnippet.snippet:
const size = value =>
  Array.isArray(value)
    ? value.length
    : value && typeof value === 'object'
      ? value.size || value.length || Object.keys(value).length
      : typeof value === 'string' ? new Blob([value]).size : 0;
